seo_description: He married her under a secret identity and supported her rise to success — only to be repaid with betrayal. On her birthday, he was publicly humiliated and cast out by her avaricious sister and her scheming conspirators. Just then, his true identity was revealed… and at that very moment, his powerful fiancée from Yanjing made a dramatic entrance!
